Add support for MultiverseCore API v5 (#1807)

Add MLX support and refactor model architecture (#23)

This PR introduces support for the MLX framework and refactors the model
architecture to accommodate both PyTorch and MLX implementations. The
changes include:

- Added new `mlx` directory with MLX-specific model and training
implementations
- Refactored the existing PyTorch model into `nue/model/torch.py`
- Created a new base `GPTConfig` class in `nue/model/base.py` for shared
configuration
- Updated the CLI to support choosing between PyTorch and MLX frameworks
- Added new GitHub Actions workflow for MLX-specific CI on macOS
- Updated dependencies to include MLX as an optional extra
